The '''''Universal Encyclopedia''''' was an illustrated reference book. [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] kept a copy in [[Ben Kenobi's home/Legends|his hut]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]], which he showed to [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] while they discussed the various [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]] of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

